# GSBOR Site Design Guide

## Design Philosophy

The Greater Springfield Board of REALTORS® website embodies **professional elegance with approachable warmth**. The design balances corporate credibility with human connection, reflecting the organization's 90+ year legacy while maintaining modern accessibility and user experience standards.

## Visual Identity

### Color Palette

**Primary Colors:**
- `primary-900`: #000000 (Deep navy/black for high-contrast text)
- `primary-800`: #111620 (Dark navy for backgrounds)
- `primary-700`: #18253b (Primary action color)
- `primary-600`: #1d3557 (Core brand navy)
- `primary-500`: #1d3557 (Default primary)
- `primary-400`: #1d3557 (Medium navy)
- `primary-300`: #55627e (Light navy)
- `primary-200`: #8b93a7 (Muted blue-gray)
- `primary-100`: #c4c8d2 (Very light blue-gray)
- `primary-50`: #ffffff (White)

**Secondary Colors:**
- `secondary-700`: #24665d (Dark teal)
- `secondary-500`: #2a9d8f (Core teal - trust and stability)
- `secondary-400`: #2a9d8f (Medium teal)

**Accent Colors:**
- `tertiary-500`: #000000 (Pure black for contrast)
- `accent-500`: #e9c46a (Warm gold for highlights)
- Green CTA: #139E78 (Vibrant green for primary actions)

### Typography

**Font Stack:**
- **Headings**: Poppins, Montserrat, Inter (Google Fonts)
- **Body**: Inter (primary), Poppins (secondary)
- **Weights**: 400 (normal), 500 (medium), 600 (semibold), 700 (bold)

**Typography Hierarchy:**
- **Hero Headlines**: 5xl-6xl (48-60px), font-light with font-medium spans
- **Section Headlines**: 3xl-4xl (30-36px), font-light with font-extrabold spans
- **Card Titles**: xl-2xl (20-24px), font-medium
- **Body Text**: base-lg (16-18px), leading-relaxed
- **Captions**: sm (14px), text-gray-600

## Layout Patterns

### Grid System
- **Container**: `container mx-auto px-6` (max-width with responsive padding)
- **Hero Layout**: Two-column grid (`grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2`) with 16-unit gap
- **Content Sections**: Three-column grid (`md:grid-cols-3`) for cards and features
- **Apple-style Showcase**: Two-column grid (`md:grid-cols-2`) with minimal gaps

### Spacing Scale
- **Section Padding**: `py-16` to `py-24` (64-96px vertical)
- **Component Spacing**: `gap-8` to `gap-16` (32-64px)
- **Element Margins**: `mb-6` to `mb-16` (24-64px)
- **Inner Padding**: `p-6` to `p-8` (24-32px)

## Component Patterns

### Hero Section Architecture
```
Hero Structure:
├── Layered Background System
│   ├── Base gradient (white to primary-50)
│   ├── Opacity overlay (gray-50/80)
│   ├── Hero image (opacity-10)
│   └── Subtle grid pattern (opacity-5)
├── Content Grid (2-column)
│   ├── Text Content (order-2 lg:order-1)
│   └── Visual Content (order-1 lg:order-2)
└── Stats Bar (backdrop-blur card)
```

**Key Elements:**
- **Layered backgrounds** with multiple opacity overlays
- **Floating decorative elements** with blur effects
- **Backdrop-blur cards** for modern glass-morphism
- **Transform hover effects** (scale-[1.02])
- **Rounded corners** consistently use `rounded-xl` to `rounded-2xl`

### Card Design System

**Standard Card Pattern:**
```css
.card-base {
  @apply bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm;
  @apply transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-500;
}

.card-elevated {
  @apply bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl;
  @apply shadow-xl border border-primary-700/30;
}

.card-dark {
  @apply bg-primary-800/40 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl;
  @apply border border-primary-700/30 shadow-xl;
}
```

### Button System

**Primary Actions:**
- Solid primary buttons: `bg-primary-700 hover:bg-primary-800`
- Rounded corners: `rounded-full` for CTAs, `rounded-md` for forms
- Consistent padding: `px-8 py-3` for large, `px-4 py-2` for medium

**Secondary Actions:**
- Outline style with backdrop-blur: `bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm`
- Link style with chevron icons for "Learn more" actions

## Visual Effects & Interactions

### Backdrop Effects
- **Glass-morphism**: `bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md`
- **Dark glass**: `bg-primary-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm`
- **Overlay gradients**: `bg-gradient-to-t from-primary-900/40 to-transparent`

### Decorative Elements
- **Floating blurred circles**: Positioned absolutely with `blur-3xl`
- **Gradient overlays**: Multi-layer gradients for depth
- **Pattern grids**: Subtle `pattern-grid` class with 20px spacing
- **Transform effects**: `hover:scale-[1.02]` for cards, `group-hover:translate-x-1` for icons

### Animation Principles
- **Duration**: `duration-500` for major transitions, `duration-300` for micro-interactions
- **Easing**: Default Tailwind easing (ease-in-out)
- **Hover states**: Consistent scale and shadow changes
- **Focus states**: Ring-based focus indicators

## Section Design Patterns

### 1. Hero Section
- **Background**: Layered with image, gradients, and patterns
- **Layout**: Asymmetric two-column with visual hierarchy
- **CTA Placement**: Primary and secondary buttons side-by-side
- **Stats Integration**: Floating stats bar with backdrop-blur

### 2. About Section (Dark Theme)
- **Background**: Dark primary with decorative elements
- **Content**: Side-by-side text and image card
- **Typography**: Light font weights with bold spans
- **Links**: Underline-on-hover with chevron icons

### 3. Events Section (Light Theme)
- **Background**: Clean white with subtle shadows
- **Layout**: Three-column card grid
- **Images**: Consistent aspect ratios with gradient overlays
- **Actions**: Link-style buttons with trailing icons

### 4. Apple-Inspired Membership Section
- **Background**: Gradient from gray-100 to white
- **Cards**: Large rounded corners (`rounded-[2rem]`)
- **Layout**: 2x2 grid with consistent spacing
- **CTA**: Full-width green banner with decorative background

### 5. Real Estate Areas (Dark Theme)
- **Background**: Rich dark with multiple decorative elements
- **Cards**: Transparent dark cards with hover glow effects
- **Icons**: Lucide icons with consistent sizing
- **Spacing**: Generous padding for breathing room

## Image Treatment

### Image Specifications
- **Aspect Ratios**: 16:9 for hero images, 4:3 for cards
- **Quality**: High-resolution Unsplash images (800px+ width)
- **Overlays**: Gradient overlays for text readability
- **Hover Effects**: Subtle scale transforms (`hover:scale-105`)

### Image Sources Pattern
- Real estate photography from Unsplash
- Professional, modern aesthetic
- Consistent color grading (warm, inviting tones)
- Focus on architectural details and lifestyle

## Responsive Design Principles

### Breakpoint Strategy
- **Mobile-first**: Base styles for mobile, enhance for larger screens
- **Key breakpoints**: `md:` (768px), `lg:` (1024px), `xl:` (1280px)
- **Grid adaptation**: Single column on mobile, multi-column on desktop
- **Typography scaling**: Responsive text sizes with `text-base md:text-lg`

### Mobile Optimizations
- **Touch targets**: Minimum 44px for buttons
- **Spacing reduction**: Smaller padding and margins on mobile
- **Image stacking**: Vertical layout for image-text combinations
- **Navigation**: Simplified mobile navigation patterns

## Accessibility Standards

### Color Contrast
- **Text on white**: Minimum 4.5:1 ratio (primary-700 and darker)
- **Text on dark**: White text on primary-800+ backgrounds
- **Interactive elements**: Clear focus states with ring utilities

### Typography Accessibility
- **Line height**: `leading-relaxed` (1.625) for body text
- **Font sizes**: Minimum 16px for body text
- **Hierarchy**: Clear heading structure (h1-h6)

## Brand Voice in Design

### Visual Personality
- **Professional**: Clean layouts, consistent spacing, quality imagery
- **Trustworthy**: Dark navy primary color, established typography
- **Approachable**: Rounded corners, warm accent colors, friendly imagery
- **Modern**: Backdrop-blur effects, subtle animations, contemporary layouts

### Content Presentation
- **Hierarchy**: Clear information architecture with visual weight
- **Scannability**: Generous whitespace, bullet points, clear sections
- **Credibility**: Statistics prominently displayed, professional photography
- **Action-oriented**: Clear CTAs with descriptive button text

## Implementation Guidelines

### CSS Architecture
- **Utility-first**: Tailwind CSS v4 with custom color variables
- **Component classes**: Minimal custom CSS, prefer utility combinations
- **Responsive utilities**: Mobile-first responsive design
- **Custom properties**: CSS variables for brand colors

### Performance Considerations
- **Image optimization**: WebP format, lazy loading, size attributes
- **Animation performance**: Transform and opacity changes only
- **Bundle optimization**: Code splitting for non-critical components
- **Loading states**: Suspense boundaries with fallback UI

### Maintenance Standards
- **Consistency**: Reuse established patterns and components
- **Documentation**: Comment complex utility combinations
- **Testing**: Cross-browser and device testing for all components
- **Accessibility**: Regular accessibility audits and testing

